    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for all my daily trips. It\u2019s been well-loved and is totally ready for its next adventure with a new owner! If you're looking for a dependable ride that still looks great on the road, this is the one for you. Feel free to message me\u2014I'd love to chat and show it to you!",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
