      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a driver-spec E92 M3 featuring the S65B40 naturally aspirated 4.0L V8, a masterpiece of engineering with an 8,400 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. This unit is paired with a longitudinal 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock for optimal torque distribution. The chassis remains sharp, equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and multi-link rear suspension for precise kinematic response. Preventive maintenance has been prioritized, including recent rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators to mitigate common S65 failure points. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the mechanical synchronization and subframe rigidity are excellent, ensuring a visceral, high-revving analog experience.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Reliable performance. Clean interior. Minimal exterior wear. Mechanically sound.",
      "price": 28500.0,
